Right?

568
00:35:42,670 --> 00:35:43,320
Go ahead.

569
00:35:44,760 --> 00:35:47,630
I asked your mother
to leave you some food and dishes.

570
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:49,290
Come back and have some early.

571
