580
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,670
I know that

581
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:40,360
I've done many wrong things lately.

582
00:36:41,510 --> 00:36:42,680
I hope Uncle Yu

583
00:36:44,110 --> 00:36:44,970
