584
00:36:49,920 --> 00:36:53,050
Take good care of yourself
when you reach the southwest.

585
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,030
The world is vast.

586
00:36:55,230 --> 00:36:56,230
Even in exile,

587
00:36:56,440 --> 00:36:58,320
