611
00:39:19,440 --> 00:39:20,710
I came to see you off.

612
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,410
Take good care of yourself.

613
00:39:26,190 --> 00:39:27,030
You too.

614
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,590
I heard the Li family

615
