660
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:07,230
and a bright future.

661
00:42:08,590 --> 00:42:10,280
in this life.

662
00:42:15,590 --> 00:42:16,920
I have no regrets

663
00:42:18,510 --> 00:42:20,510
